def max_accordion_length(s: str) -> int:
    n = len(s)
    p1 = s.find('[')
    p2 = s.find(':', p1)
    p4 = s.rfind(']')
    p3 = s.rfind(':', p2, p4)
    if p1 <= p2 < p3 < p4:
        k = s[p2 + 1:p3].count('|')
        return k + 4
    else:
        return -1
